    <strong>**Privacy Policy for Cypher Range Vinyl**</strong>

    Effective Date: 9/13/2023

    <strong>**1. Introduction**</strong>

    Welcome to Cypher Range Vinyl! This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your personal information when you interact with our vinyl record shop, owned by Darlene Duyn ("we," "us," or "our"). We value your privacy and are committed to safeguarding your personal information.

    <strong>**2. Information We Collect**</strong>

    We may collect various types of personal information when you visit our website or shop. This information may include:

    - Contact information (e.g., name, email address, phone number).
    - Shipping and billing address for record orders.
    - Payment information (e.g., credit card details) for transactions.
    - Records of your interactions with us (e.g., purchase history, customer service inquiries).
    - Website usage information (e.g., IP address, browser type, cookies, and tracking technologies).

    <strong>**3. How We Use Your Information**</strong>

    We use the information we collect for the following purposes:

    - To fulfill and manage your record orders.
    - To communicate with you about your orders and provide customer support.
    - To send you promotional and marketing materials (only if you've opted in).
    - To improve our website and services.
    - To comply with legal requirements and protect our rights and interests.

    <strong>**4. Information Sharing**</strong>

    We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. However, we may share your information with trusted service providers who assist us in operating our website and business. These service providers are obligated to maintain the confidentiality and security of your information.

    **5. Cookies and Tracking Technologies**

    We use cookies and similar technologies to enhance your browsing experience on our website. You can manage cookie preferences through your web browser settings.

    <strong>**6. Your Choices**</strong>

    You have the following choices regarding your personal information:

    - You can opt-out of receiving marketing communications from us.
    - You can access and update your personal information by contacting us.
    - You can request the deletion of your personal information (subject to legal obligations).

    <strong>**7. Security**</strong>

    We take appropriate measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.

    <strong>**8. Children's Privacy**</strong>

    Our services are not directed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect or maintain personal information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe we have collected information from your child, please contact us to request its removal.

    <strong>**9. Changes to This Privacy Policy**</strong>

    We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. The most recent version will always be available on our website.

    <strong>**10. Contact Us**</strong>

    If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy or your personal information, please contact us at:

    Cypher Range Vinyl
    cyphermail@gmail.com
    

    Thank you for choosing Cypher Range Vinyl. We appreciate your trust in us and are dedicated to protecting your privacy and providing a secure and enjoyable shopping experience.
